    <scopecontent id="ref1" encodinganalog="description">
      <p>Photocopies of handwritten letters. The items are correspondence between members of the F. G. Wilson family who lived in Mesa, Arizona; Santaquin, Utah; and Wasatch County, Utah. Most of the items were written in the 1880s and deal with family matters. Genealogical materials for the Wilson family are also included.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <bioghist id="ref2" encodinganalog="description">
